.formypeople.org/dream/70-the-tree-the-wood-the-truth/" itemprop="url">70. The Tree, the Wood, the Truth</a></li>\n<li id="menu-item-19419" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-dream menu-item-19419"><a href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/71-submission-a-message-for-today/" itemprop="url">71. Submission: A Message for Today</a></li>\n<li id="menu-item-20212" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-dream menu-item-20212"><a href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/72-leaders-in-cloaks-and-masks/" itemprop="url">72. Leaders in Cloaks and Masks</a></li>\n<li id="menu-item-20539" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-dream menu-item-20539"><a href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/73-the-universal-memorial/" itemprop="url">73. The Universal Memorial</a></li>\n</ul></div><div class="clear"></div>\n\t\t\t<style>\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573 {  }\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573 ul.wpsm-arrow-enabled:before {  } \n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573 ul, #short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573 ul ul {  }\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573 a {  }\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573 a:hover {  }\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573 ul a {  }\n\t\t\t\t#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573 ul a:hover {  }\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t</style>\n\t\t\t<script type="text/javascript">\n\t\t\t\tvar show_arrow = "true";var $sm = jQuery.noConflict();\n\t\t\t\t\tjQuery(function ($) {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$("#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573").tinyNav();\n\t\t\t\t\t\t$("#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573").next().addClass("shortcode-menu-mobile");\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tshortcode_menu_responsive();\n\t\t\t\t\t});\n\t\t\t\t\tjQuery(window).resize(function($){\n\t\t\t\t\t\tshortcode_menu_responsive();\n\t\t\t\t\t});\n\t\t\t\t\tfunction shortcode_menu_responsive()\n\t\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tvar window_width = $sm(window).width();\n\t\t\t\t\t\tif(window_width <= 650)\n\t\t\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t$sm("#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573").hide();\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t$sm("#short_menu_5b8b16a5cd573").